quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  22,60,"Ke kamoo ho leng kateng. Mong le mong ea iphetetsang ka bohloko bo ts’oanang le boo a ileng a bo utloisoa, e be hamorao o boetse o phetoa ka bona, Ruri! Allah U tla mo thusa. Hobane! Allah ke Eena Ea tlosang libe, o ts’oarela- joalo-joalo"
  22,61,"Ke hobane Allah U entse hore bosiu bo sehe mots’eare tsebe le mots’eare o sehe bosiu tsebe, hobane Allah U ultoa tsohle, U bona tsohle"
  22,62,"Hobane Allah – Ke ‘Nete, seo ba bitsang ho sona kantle ho Eena, ke leshano, Allah U Phahametse Tsohle, U Moholo- Holo"
  22,63,"Na ha le bone kamoo Allah A romellang pula lefats’eng kateng e tsoa marung, ebe lefats’e le apareloa ke botala ka letsatsi le hlahlamang? Ruri! Allah U Hloekile, U Hlokolosi"
  22,64,"Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le lefats’eng ke tsa Hae. Ruri! Allah ha A hloke letho, U ts’oanetsoe ke lithoriso tsohle"
  22,65,"Na ha le bone kamoo Allah A entseng hore lintho tsohle tse teng lefats’eng li be le molemo kateng ho lona? Likepe li sesa holim’a leoatle ka taelo ea Hae, U ts’oere leholimo hore le se ke la oela fats’e kantle le ka tumello ea Hae. Ruri! Allah U Tletse Khauhelo, U Mohau o Khaphatsehang ho batho"
  22,66,"Ke Eena ea le nehileng bophelo, ke Eena ea tla etsa hore le shoe, A boele A le nehe bophelo hape. Ruri! Motho ke sebupuoa se hlokang teboho"
  22,67,"Re fane ka lits’ebeletso tsa keteko le meetlo ho lichaba tsohle tseo ba ts’oanetseng ho li phethahatsa; ba se u ngangise ka taba eo, empa u ba biletse ho Mong`a hau. Hobane! Ruri uena u latetse Tataiso e Nepahetseng"
  22,68,"Empa ba u phehisa khang, E re: “Allah U tseba ka botlalo tsohle tseo le li etsang"
  22,69,“Allah U tla ahlola lipakeng tsa lona mohla Letsatsi la Kahlolo khahlanong le seo le neng le hanyetsana ka sona
  22,70,"Na ha le tsebe hore Allah U tseba lintho tsohle tse leholimong esita le tsohle tse lefats’eng? Ruri! Seo se ngoliloe, seo se bobebe ho Allah"
  22,71,"Empa ba khumamela lintho tse sa kang tsa senoleloa matla le hanyane, kantle ho Allah, tse bileng li senang le tsebo. Baetsalibe ha ba na mothusi"
  22,72,"Ha Lits’enolo tsa Rona tse Hlakileng li phetoa, u tla bona tatolo lifahlehong tsa mahana-tumelo; ho sale hanyane ba futuhela ba ba phetelang lits’enolo tsa Rona. E re: “Na nka le bolella ka se seng se nyarosang ho feta lits’enolo seo? Ke Mollo! Oo Allah a o ts’episitseng mahana-tumelo. Phello ea leeto e babang"
  22,73,"Oho batho! Papiso ke ena, kahoo thehang tsebe: Lintho tseo le li bitsang ho tsona ntle ho Allah li sitoa ho hlola leha e le ts’ints’i, le ha li ka kopano ‘moho ka morero oo. Haeba ts’ints’i e ka nka ho hong ho tsona, li ke ke tsa e pholosa ho eona. Kahoo, ka bobeli bakopi le bakopuoang ba ea fokola"
  22,74,"Ba mpa ba entse tekanyo ka Allah: Hobane! Ruri Allah ke Ea Matla, Ea phethahatsang Thato ea Hae"
  22,75,"Allah U khetha baromuoa har’a manyeloi le har’a batho. Allah ke Eena Ea utloang tsohle, o bona tsohle"
  22,76,"U tseba tsohle tse kapel’a bona esita le tsohle tse kamora’ bona, lipotso tsohle li tla boela ho Allah"
  22,77,"Oho lona ba kholoang! Inamang, le ithapalatse le rapele Mong`a lona, le etse ka toka, hore le tle le atlehe"
  22,78,"Le be le tsitlalle tseleng ea Allah joaloka ha e le tokelo ea hae ho tsitlallela. U le khethile, ha A le belesa ka mojaro o boima tumelong; ke tumelo ea ntat’a lona Abrahama. Ke eena ea le rehileng Mamuslim linakong tsa khale-khale le ka har’a"